title: Icon not given
body: Im not sure if this is supposed to be on Misc, but i didn't recieve an icon. But i did recieve the skin! Anyone else here like me?{{champion:32}}

replies.body: We're still in the process of handing them out! You should have them on or by September 23rd. Hang tight! ^-^
I Didn't Get it ;-; its September 24.
The gifts are still being handed out, and the final date to receive them has been moved to the 30th, as per the banner on the [support page](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us).
